# Heading

This test is checking heading related features.

* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

`djotfmt` always make sure there is one blank line after heading.

## This is a level 2 heading

# A blank line should be inserted above this level 1 heading

### Another blank line should be inserted above this level 3 heading

* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

`djotfmt` remove strip multiple blank lines before and after heading to
one.

### There should be only one blank line below this level 3 heading

## There should be only one blank line above this level 2 heading

* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

`djotfmt` indent multiple lines of heading text to align with the first
non-space character of the first line.

### This is a very long long long long long long long long long long
    long long long long long long long long long long long long long
    long long long long long long long long long heading that should be
    wrapped to multiple lines
